Description: The two accessories included with the system are seated in a pocket on the back of the system until use. The following is a list of the two accessoriesDiamond Dermabrasion Skin Scrubber 1.Connect all associated components: a.Unscrew the Diamond Vacuum Output socket and ensure a large cotton filter is in the center and a large black ring is around connector head. b.Replace the Diamond Vacuum Output socket. c.Attach one end of the PVC hose to the Diamond Vacuum Output socket. d.Attach the other end of the PVC hose to the end of the diamond-tipped wand. e.Ensure a small black ring is around the head of the wand. f.Place a small cotton filter on the head of wand. g.Select the appropriate diamond tip size and screw it into the wand. If necessary, refer to Table 1 for recommended diamond tip usage. 2.Connect the plug to the Power Cord connector, plug in, and press the power button. 3.Turn the Vacuum Intensity Knob to the lowest setting. 4.Slowly increase the vacuum intensity to the desired setting (see Table 1 for recommendations). The Vacuum Meter will display the amount of pressure. In general, the maximum vacuum intensity should only be used when necessary. 5.Using a slow sliding motion, move the diamond tipped wand across the skin. Refer to the “Treatment” section of Chapter 3 of this guide for details about how to use the system to treat specific areas of the face and body. Important: Do not leave the diamond tip in one area for an extended period of time. Doing so may damage to the skin. 6.Using your thumb and finger, gently stretch the skin of the treatment area and glide the wand two or three more times over the area. Note: Crisscrossing your movements is recommended to prevent streaking. You may use brush strokes or polishing motions in different areas of the skin being treated. 7.When the treatment is complete, use a soft brush to remove any dead skin and rinse the treated area with a damp sponge or a cool, damp towel. 8.Allow the skin to dry and then apply desired skin product. 9.Use a toothbrush or cotton swab dabbed in alcohol to clean the diamond tip. 10.Sterilize diamond tip with ultraviolet light or high temperatureThe Diamond Dermabrasion function includes two stainless steel wands that may be used with nine interchangeable diamond tips.Important Notes about the Diamond Tips:Diamond tips provide finer grit the higher their “D” number. For example, the D100 diamond tip provides a finer grit than the D80 diamond tip. The diamond tips must be sterilized before use. The recommended sterilization process is to first clean the tips with alcohol, and then by expose them to ultraviolet light or high temperature. Replace the large cotton filter, which is located inside the vacuum connector, every five treatments. Replace the small cotton filter after each treatment.

Description: Please be assured to use them and make your own design of your nail pattern.How to use: When you get this pen, Simply shake the bottle well before use and pump the tip until the color starts to flow. Find a stiff flat surface and press the nib.( pen point is flexible and you can press It like a switch) Then cover the lid and swing it several times, you will see the color runs to the lid. Easy huh? If the first time the water is not enough, just cover the lid and swing more times. Very simple, everybody can control it.

Title: Revlon Nail Enamel(Green Sheen)
STZ nail sticker
Description: New design nail stickers, beautiful and easy to use. These stickers look so cute and gorgeous on any color nail varnish. It looks beautiful over any light colour nail polish, especially white colour. These stickers are very popular and high in demand in USA, Uk, Russia etc.One sheet of adhesive nail art stickers to fit all fingernails, toenails and nail tips.No glue required and easy to remove. Just wipe it with cotton dabbed with nail polish remover.How to apply nail water decals :1. Trim, clean and polish the fingernails with your favourite colour nail polish.Tip : light colours preferred. Especially white colour nail polish.2. Let the nail polish dry completely.3. Remove the transparent film of the product, cut out the pattern and plunge it into water for around 15-20 seconds.4. Take the sticker out from water and slide the pattern from backing paper with the help of fingers.5. Moisten the fingernail, stick the pattern in position.Tip : you can move the sticker on finger by sliding it with the help of fingers.6. Dry up the water on fingernail with the help of paper towel and blow dry.7. Cap the design with nail polish top coat and blow dry. Don’t forget to seal the edge.8. Enjoy your new creation. :)
